    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Libero Pa<lb break="no" n="2"/>tri <expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Rena<lb break="no" n="3"/>tus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>XIII <expan><abbr>gem</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> voto <lb n="5"/>libens posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In vier Fragmente gebrochen. Datierung: Der Tempel befindet sich auf den Befestigungsmauern des Municipium Aurelium.</p>
            </div>
